title: BlackAcre #9 / #10 [IMAGE Comics]
description:
BlackAcre #9 / #10 [IMAGE Comics]

#9:
A high risk ploy has landed a pair of assassins deep in the heart of enemy territory. And now theyre closing in on the target. But how much longer will their cover - and their luck - hold?

#10:
At his distant outpost, Hull receives unwelcome visitors. Meanwhile, an eager Guardian puts BlackAcres security capabilities on explosive display.
